  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_36",
    "english": "Taimanin, Gosha Academy student. An elite, strict and rigid. A talented figure who is literally a \"surefire\".\n\nUses a special ninja art called \"Paper Spirit\" which puts Particles into paper and enhances them. It is a highly adaptive ninja art that is capable of dealing with various situations such as snaring enemies or transforming into blades or explosives.",
